# ğŸ” Metasploitable2 Vulnerability Assessment & Penetration Testing (VAPT)

A complete Vulnerability Assessment & Penetration Testing (VAPT) project performed on **Metasploitable2**, an intentionally vulnerable Linux-based virtual machine used for penetration testing practice.  
This project follows a real-world VAPT workflow including **Passive Recon, Active Recon, Enumeration, Vulnerability Analysis, Exploitation, Privilege Escalation**, and **Reporting**.

---

# ğŸ“Œ Project Objectives
- Perform complete VAPT on Metasploitable2
- Identify open ports, services, and vulnerabilities
- Exploit misconfigurations & known CVEs
- Gain system access and escalate privileges
- Generate a professional VAPT report

